# OpenJournal Environment Configuration
#
# API keys are loaded from environment variables in the following priority:
# 1. OPENJOURNAL_DEEPSEEK_API_KEY (highest priority)
# 2. DEEPSEEK_API_KEY
#
# API keys are NEVER stored in the OpenJournal SQLite database.
# They are either loaded from environment variables or saved to the
# OS credential manager via the app's AI Settings UI.

# DeepSeek API key (default AI provider)
# OPENJOURNAL_DEEPSEEK_API_KEY=sk-your-key-here

# Fallback DeepSeek API key
# DEEPSEEK_API_KEY=sk-your-key-here
